      Very
 nice phone. I paid $350 for refurbished and am enjoying it. I have seen
 elsewhere for $600-$800 and it is not worth that. The set up was 
extremely easy and the apps all work well. Great for every day though 
battery is less than half charged by the time I leave work, and that is 
with light use only. If you are the average user, this phone works. If 
you're on the phone all day, I would suggest something with a longer 
battery life.
